sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Analyst
    participant UI as Streamlit UI
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Service as Ticket Workflow Service
    participant Graph as LangGraph
    participant RAG as RAG Service
    participant Safety as Safety Layer
    participant Approval as Approval Service
    participant Audit as Audit Service

    User->>UI: Submit ticket
    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/tickets/analyze
    API->>Service: Validate and start workflow
    Service->>Audit: Record workflow_started
    Service->>Graph: Invoke graph with run_id and ticket
    Graph->>Graph: intake
    Graph->>Graph: classify
    Graph->>RAG: retrieve relevant sources
    RAG-->>Graph: chunks, citations, scores, injection flags
    Graph->>Graph: reason
    Graph->>Graph: draft_solution
    Graph->>Safety: safety_check
    Safety-->>Graph: findings, command risk, grounding status
    Graph->>Graph: final_answer
    Graph-->>Service: final state
    Service->>Approval: Create pending approvals for proposed actions
    Approval->>Audit: Record approval_created
    Service->>Audit: Record workflow_completed
    Service-->>API: Final response
    API-->>UI: Answer, citations, commands, approvals
    UI-->>User: Display result and approval controls
    User->>UI: Approve or reject suggested action
    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/approvals/{id}/decision
    API->>Approval: Store decision
    Approval->>Audit: Record approval_decision
    API-->>UI: Updated approval status
